    {
      "paragraph_name": "COPAU0AO",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This data structure redefines the COPAU0AI structure to allow access to individual characters within certain fields. Specifically, it provides character-by-character access to the transaction name (TRNNAMEC, TRNNAMEP, TRNNAMEH, TRNNAMEV, TRNNAMEO), title (TITLE01C, TITLE01P, TITLE01H, TITLE01V, TITLE01O), and current date (CURDATEC). This redefinition is useful for manipulating individual characters within these fields, such as for validation or formatting purposes. The filler fields ensure proper alignment with the corresponding fields in COPAU0AI. This structure is likely used in conjunction with COPAU0AI to provide more granular control over the data being displayed or processed.",
